3
00:00:05.970 --> 00:00:09.270
as well as data transfer out of AWS.

4
00:00:09.270 --> 00:00:12.990
So if you take data from AWS onto your Snowball Edge

5
00:00:12.990 --> 00:00:15.750
and then you receive it, then you're going to pay for this.

6
00:00:15.750 --> 00:00:19.710
